snippet.textDisplay: In a month, I'll be returning to college. I'm a violinist. I've always wanted to help people with my music, but I still don't know how. Last year, I suffered a lot. Anxiety took over. It was my first year, and it was really hard. I couldn't go to class, or even get out of bed. It was really hard. The violin became an enemy. Also, my favorite person left me, abandoned me, and scorned me. It was like being stabbed. Because of this, I want to help all those people who suffer in silence through my music. I have to figure out how to do it. Your channel inspires me. Thank you. ü©∑
